    "There he focused on the materialist theories of art history.": [],
    "He moved to Strasbourg as professor at the university of Strasbourg in 1936.": [],
    "At Strasbourg, he continued to concentrate on the social production of art, weaving a combination of political, religious and scientific history into his writing.": [],
